# LOCATE

MISSION DIRECTIVE: Detection services have identified an incoming fleet originating from sector G-9-35-Alpha. Focus all analysis on that sector. We have indications this may be a hostile fleet intent on invasion.

Command needs an exact count on the number of approaching vessels to initiate appropriate countermeasures. Intelligence has relayed that Motherships can be identified by their unique green color. Fighters are identified by their blue color. Red indicates a sun, which does not count as a vessel.

## INPUT
The input will be a series of Base64 encoded images, one per line. 

## The Output
Print the number of ships detected in each image, ignoring any suns.

## Sample output
52
